title: State Fair Crits
description: State Fair Crit 1.  This will be the first in a three consecutive Tuesday training series.  Prizes, fields and duration are yet to be decided.
course: The course will be a 6 turn L shaped crit course less than one mile.
registration: Register at Sports base online.  This event may fill up.  Please register online.
notes: This course has been a gem of the MN cycling scene for a long time.  For years it has been put on hold due to the high costs of using the fairgrounds.  Cat 6 will be taking some risks to promote this race.  We believe it is the perfect venue and are only trying to break even on the event.  The fees are a bit higher for a training race, but we believe the course and the proximity are worth it.  Please also consider helping us with some fundraising for the event.
